strings: <voice_0x01000FEC><se_low>King of tricks: At least we can finally kick this evil brother out!
<voice_0x01000FED><se_low>King of tricks: Yes, we have come such a long way. Looking back on these difficult times, I feel a strange sense of nostalgia.
<voice_0x01000FEE><se_low>King of tricks: But this is not the time to remember friends! This is our opportunity! Dormagos is a bit odd now.
<voice_0x01000FEF><se_low>King of tricks: You will have to defeat him for a long time in order to remove the curse from this demon!
<voice_0x01000FF0><se_low>King of tricks: We are here for you, we are sure that you will not have any problems!
